title: Edison Welcomes Carlisle and Smith to Darke County Campus (Edison Community College)
text: ( Source : Edison Community College ) Edison State Community College is pleased to welcome Rachel Carlisle and Cassie Smith to the Darke County Campus . Carlisle has joined the campus as an Enrollment Manager while Smith has joined as a College
